				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/B%C3%A1t-mu%E1%BB%99n/poem-_3trYeu7UK2Z6kJllb-KaA">Bát muộn - 撥悶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/H%E1%BA%A3o-li%E1%BB%85u-ca-ch%C3%BA/poem-6HMc4oIz_l7i-7ZKwrHtVg">Hảo liễu ca chú - 好了歌注</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/Hi%E1%BB%83u-h%C3%A0nh-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-b%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%97-quy%C3%AAn-hoa/poem-ZlqSrRTS_gRBvVQh3CuIVw">Hiểu hành đạo bàng đỗ quyên hoa - 曉行道旁杜鵑花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/author-JSRpfYAHfq-c4bVKwnYGVg">Dương Vạn Lý</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/H%C6%B0-hoa-ng%E1%BB%99/poem-DB1C01n90wml4YUiZ18_Lg">Hư hoa ngộ - 虛花悟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAm-T%C3%BAc/Ng%C5%A9-b%C3%A1ch-ni%C3%AAn-tang-%C4%91i%E1%BB%81n-th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-h%E1%BA%A3i/poem-id9GNKL1A7LJdXZaTrTjcw">Ngũ bách niên tang điền thương hải - 五百年桑田滄海</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAm-T%C3%BAc/author-n1sXcnoer4D2yKNe3UaYfw">Diêm Túc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Ni%E1%BB%87m-Ph%E1%BA%ADt-ng%C3%A2m/poem-GCP9PF9V72IlLhrwhRqbGg">Niệm Phật ngâm - 念佛吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/S%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-v%E1%BA%A5n-%C4%91%C3%A1p/poem-SK_y8wVucpWN9zKU-mphNw">Sư đệ vấn đáp - 師弟問答</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-EY7jN0xHQfiiJpD91KwIgw">Trần Nhân Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/T%E1%BA%A3o-mai-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-ekjgWfNzYaR2dtLmQkchqQ">Tảo mai kỳ 1 - 早梅其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-EY7jN0xHQfiiJpD91KwIgw">Trần Nhân Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-Cai/Ti%E1%BB%83u-%C4%91%C3%A0o-h%E1%BB%93ng/poem-Y_ws2BgIHG03b0kFxaY-AQ">Tiểu đào hồng - 小桃紅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-Cai/author-IEY1qp52H1ytxgP5URFeAw">Trình Cai</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%E1%BB%A8c-t%C3%ADch-h%C3%A0nh/poem-ge3roxY_wTnhX9otjRtWWw">Ức tích hành - 憶昔行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
